title: LibreOffice 7.6.2 and 7.5.7 Released to Address Critical WebP Vulnerability
description:
LibreOffice 7.6.2 and LibreOffice 7.5.7 are now available for download to address a critical security vulnerability in the WebP codec. All users are urged to update as soon as possible.

title: Firefox 119 Promises to Let You Import Some of Your Chrome Extensions
description:
Firefox 119 web browser is now available for public beta testing with support for importing Chrome extensions when migrating from Google Chrome, an improved Firefox View feature, and more.
